"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">b</span> : <span class=\"fn\">B</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\">(<span class=\"fn\">F₁</span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Algebra/Module/LinearMap.html#ContinuousLinearMap\">→SL[</a><span class=\"fn\">σ</span><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Algebra/Module/LinearMap.html#ContinuousLinearMap\">]</a> <span class=\"fn\">F₂</span>) <a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Algebra/Module/LinearMap.html#ContinuousLinearMap\">→L[</a><span class=\"fn\">𝕜₂</span><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Algebra/Module/LinearMap.html#ContinuousLinearMap\">]</a> <span class=\"fn\">F₁</span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Algebra/Module/LinearMap.html#ContinuousLinearMap\">→SL[</a><span class=\"fn\">σ</span><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Algebra/Module/LinearMap.html#ContinuousLinearMap\">]</a> <span class=\"fn\">F₂</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Assume `eᵢ` and `eᵢ'` are trivializations of the bundles `Eᵢ` over base `B` with fiber `Fᵢ`\n(`i ∈ {1,2}`), then `Pretrivialization.continuousLinearMapCoordChange σ e₁ e₁' e₂ e₂'` is the\ncoordinate change function between the two induced (pre)trivializations\n`Pretrivialization.continuousLinearMap σ e₁ e₂` and\n`Pretrivialization.continuousLinearMap σ e₁' e₂'` of the bundle of continuous linear maps. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Topology/VectorBundle/Hom.html#Pretrivialization.continuousLinearMapCoordChange","kind":"def","line":56,"name":"Pretrivialization.continuousLinearMapCoordChange","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/Topology/VectorBundle/Hom.lean#L56-L64"}}],"imports":["Init","Mathlib.Topology.VectorBundle.Basic"],"instances":[{"className":"Pretrivialization.IsLinear","name":"Pretrivialization.continuousLinearMap.isLinear","typeNames":["Pretrivialization.continuousLinearMap"]},{"className":"TopologicalSpace","name":"Bundle.ContinuousLinearMap.topologicalSpaceTotalSpace","typeNam